name: Roger's

reviews.review_text:
Its always a great experience to have a meal at beach front with ocean talking to you with its whispers and at night with an candle light . Rogers provide the great and best food with great hospitability and service. The waiters were very humble, polite and provide an express service.

Keep up the good work.

Its worth experiencing once..!

Benaulim is a great beach and a bloody peaceful one. Rogers was a great shack experience. Sea food was fantastic. We had a Beer and Smoke and the time they took to bring us the dishes were great. Right in front of the beach gives us a great beach view. No music and hence a peaceful place to enjoy your drink or food

One of the best beach shack experiences I ever had in Goa. Calm, Serene & Peaceful ambience located at the beautiful Benaulim beach. Had visited multiple times especially the last few months. Seating on the beach front is huge üëçüèª & it gives one a great positive vibe. Will visit again n again. Special thanks to the person named Rana who served us. Loved all their Pork cuisines. They serve alcohol as well. These are items we tried here at Roger's over the time~ Pork Vindaloo, Pork Amsole, Honey Glazed Pork, Goan Pork Sausage Chilly Fry, Butter  Naan, Peri Peri French Fries, Virgin Colada, Virgin Mary Mocktail, Avocado Shake (loved it), Teriyaki Chicken Sizzler, Prawns Masala Fry.

description:
Nestled along the serene shores of Benaulim, Goa, Roger's has quickly become a beloved dining destination. With an impressive rating of 4.3 stars derived from 2,659 reviews, this beach shack encapsulates the quintessential Goan experience, combining delightful cuisine with breathtaking views. Popular tags such as "beach," "shack," "candle," and "sunset" reflect the vibrant atmosphere and culinary specialties that keep patrons returning for more.

### Ambiance & Design
As you approach Roger's, you are instantly greeted by its picturesque beachfront setting where sand meets sea. The rustic charm of this beach shack radiates an inviting warmth, especially at night when candlelight flickers against the backdrop of a starry sky. The outdoor seating arrangement allows guests to relish the gentle ocean breeze, creating an idyllic escape. The photos captured by customers beautifully showcase Roger's laid-back vibe, revealing cozy tables dressed in simple yet charming d√©cor‚Äîperfect for unwinding while savoring a meal. The absence of loud music amplifies the tranquil ambiance, offering diners a peaceful retreat.

### Menu & Culinary Experience
The menu at Roger's is a celebration of Goan flavors, prominently featuring seafood that has made it a standout among locals and tourists alike. Signature dishes recommended by frequent visitors include the **Pork Vindaloo**, **Honey Glazed Pork**, and **Prawns Masala Fry**, alongside a thoughtful selection of vegetarian options. Several reviews highlighted the combination of rich spices and fresh ingredients, particularly lauding the presentations that evoke both authenticity and innovation. Diners have also enjoyed cocktails like **Virgin Colada** and **Virgin Mary Mocktail**, perfectly complementing the coastal vibe. This diverse menu accommodates various dietary preferences, making it accessible to a wider audience.

### Customer Experience & Service
The service at Roger's has garnered ample praise, with guests noting the humility and politeness of the staff, notably mentioning an exceptional server named Rana. The efficiency of service, coupled with the welcoming demeanor of the waitstaff, enhances the overall dining experience. It seems that both reservations and walk-ins are accommodated with care, ensuring that all guests feel valued and well-taken care of.

### Popularity & Reviews
The resonance of Roger's beyond its physical locale can be felt through the enthusiastic reviews that paint a picture of enjoyable times spent over excellent meals. Diners express immense satisfaction, highlighting their encounters on social media as well, which speaks volumes to its popularity. Visitors repeatedly mention their desire to return, affirming that Roger's is not just a meal but a memorable experience that beckons them back to its shores. While it may not have garnered specific critic accolades, the overwhelming sentiment from patrons speaks to its exceptional service and atmosphere.

### Utilizing Visual Content
The provided images lend credence to the compelling narrative of Roger's. They capture the inviting atmosphere‚Äîwhere beach chairs sit just feet from the lapping waves and tables adorned with candles create an intimate setting. The delectable dishes are beautifully showcased, offering a taste of the vibrant culinary offerings that await each patron.

In conclusion, Roger's in Benaulim, Goa, stands out as a charming beach shack that promises a delightful dining experience framed by the stunning sunset views. With a captivating atmosphere, remarkable food, and commendable service, it is undoubtedly a must-visit destination for anyone looking to indulge in the flavors of coastal Goa.
